## What NOT to do
- Do not add Supabase, Firebase, or any new third-party services
- Do not add TipTap, Quill, ProseMirror, or any heavy editor library — use native contentEditable
- Do not store access tokens in localStorage or sessionStorage
- Do not embed the Client Secret anywhere in frontend code
- Do not modify the existing Drive folder structure or `_index.json` schema
- Do not change the Netlify, Vite, Tailwind, or PostCSS config files

